Load and follow **.cclaw/skills/shipping-and-handoff/SKILL.md** — it contains the full checklist, examples, interaction protocol, and verification discipline.

## HARD-GATE
Do NOT merge, push, or finalize without a passed preflight check, written rollback plan, and exactly one explicit finalization mode selected. No exceptions for urgency.

## In / Out
